## Limitations
This report is based on available data and estimates, which can vary significantly depending on the methodologies and assumptions used by different organizations. The figures provided are estimates and may not account for all variables, such as geopolitical factors, climate change, and economic fluctuations. Additionally, the effectiveness of spending is contingent on efficient allocation and management of resources, which is not guaranteed.